# disable window titlebars and set no window border
# Now I am using i3-wm, having window border is easier to recognize the different window
# And also, this approach is deprecated
# https://gist.github.com/lirenlin/9892945#gistcomment-3604348
# To show titlebars, replace `pixel` with `normal`
default_border pixel 2
default_floating_border pixel 2
hide_edge_borders smart

# After released https://github.com/i3/i3/releases/tag/4.21 ,
# the following line is needed to hide titlebars
# Some discussions:
# https://github.com/i3/i3/issues/5149
# https://gist.github.com/lirenlin/9892945?permalink_comment_id=4312849#gistcomment-4312849
